[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    312[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mThe architecture finding A1 (conflicts aggregated but never rendered) is coupled tightly to the recipe's own teaching. The "Failure Modes" section names "consultant silo-ing" and "contradictions across services" as must-solve problems. The aggregation step builds the data structure. The generation step walks past it. This is not a style gap or a polish gap; it is an architecture-level omission that undermines the recipe's central argument about clinical safety. The fix strengthens the teaching rather than softening it. All experts agree on priority.[K
