[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    438[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mAmazon Athena, AWS Glue Data Catalog, and AWS Lake Formation for the audit-and-analytics surface.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m The federation attribution data, the per-query audit-event log, and the per-participant performance metrics surface through Athena queries with Lake Formation column-level and row-level access controls. Treatment-context users see the institution's own portion of the attribution chain; cross-QHIN-coordination users see the full attribution chain for dispute resolution; audit-and-compliance users see the full audit-event log; the institutional governance committee sees the federation-level metrics.[K
