[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     700[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             session_id, tool, exc)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     701[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     702[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     703[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def _redact_tool_args(arguments: dict) -> dict:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     704[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     705[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Strip sensitive fields from tool arguments before they go in
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     706[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     the ledger. The ledger keeps enough to reconstruct what
