[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m *The pseudocode calls this `verify_identity(session_id, intent, auth_context)`. Refills generally require a higher assurance floor than scheduling: many institutions allow only authenticated portal sessions for refill transmissions. The bot's identity-verification policy reflects this. Status-check-only intents may be allowed at lower assurance.*
