[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2580[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     the bucket has Object Lock in compliance mode and a retention
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2581[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     period sized to the longest of HIPAA's six-year minimum,
