[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def run_demo():
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Run a small set of end-to-end scenarios that exercise the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     main paths through the refill-bot pipeline:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       1. Happy-path auto-approval: an established patient with
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          a recent A1c on file refilling metformin.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       2. Specialist medication: an amiodarone refill request
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          routes to the cardiology office, not auto-approved.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       3. Controlled substance: an oxycodone refill request hits
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          the controlled-substance triple-defense and routes to
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          clinical, never auto-approved.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       4. Out-of-scope discontinuation: "I want to stop taking
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          my sertraline" classifies as medication_change and
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    4311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m          hands off.
